profile.private_key_text: Ngenisa isitshixo sangasese ngezantsi kunye negama lokudlula lesitshixo ukuba liyafuneka. Isitshixo sikawonke-wonke siya kukhutshwa kwiqhosha labucala. I-Passbrase ayigcinwanga.

profile.ssh_public_text: Isitshixo sikawonke-wonke esixhonywe kwiseshoni nganye entsha ye-Kasm ukuba ivunyelwe yimigaqo-nkqubo yomlawuli.
profile.theme_text: Lungisa umxholo we-APP. I-Auto iya kusebenzisa iinkqubo zendawo os umxholo.
profile.tip_text: Veza iingcebiso eziluncedo xa usungula iseshoni ye-KASM.
profile.session-usage-details-last-30-: Iinkcukacha zokusetyenziswa kweseshoni: Iintsuku ezingama-30 ezidlulileyo

settings.auth-description: Useto lweHlabathi olunxulumene nokungqinisisa kwiseva (kubandakanya ukongeza iGoogle Repaptcha kunye nezaziso kwisikrini sokungena. Hambisa ngaphezulu kwetayitile yokuseta ukuze ubone izixhobo.
settings.connections-description: Ezi seto zisetyenziselwa ukuchaza uthotho lweeparamitha zoqhagamshelo zokudibanisa ukuya kwi-RDP ye-RDP / SSH / ye-Kasmvch. Ichazwa njengentambo enye ye-json
settings.images-description: Useto lweHlabathi ukuseta ukuba longeza ukuba isebenze kwiqela le-CPU okanye hayi kwaye ukuseta indlela yokwabiwa kwe-CPU.
settings.licensing-description: Ukucwangciswa kwehlabathi ukucacisa indawo kwiseva yelayisensi
settings.logging-description: Useto lweHlabathi ukuseta ukhetho lwe-KASM. I-KASM ibonelela ngemvume ethengiswayo ebhokisini, nokuba ufaka i-Kasm yonke kwiserver enye kwi-System esasaziweyo kunye neearhente ezininzi ze-APMS, zonke iilogo ziyaqokelelwa kwaye zidityaniswe.
settings.manager-description: Useto lweHlabathi Ukumisela uMphathi, khumbula ukuqalisa kwakhona iinkonzo ukuba ziyafuneka.
settings.scale-description: Useto lweHlabathi ukumisela indlela izikali ze-KASM, kubandakanya neearhente ezenzekelayo kwaye ziqwalasele indlela ukucombulula ngayo.
settings.storage-description: Useto lweHlabathi Ukucwangcisa iinkcukacha zangaphandle zokugcina iinkcukacha zokusetyenziswa ngeKasm ngezinto ezinjengeeprofayili eziqhubekayo.
settings.theme-description: Useto lweHlabathi ukumisela umxholo ujonge, njengokumisela umfanekiso wangasemva kwidashboard yomsebenzisi.
settings.web_filter-description: Useto lweHlabathi Ukusetha icebo lewebhu, kubandakanya ukubeka indawo yefilitha yeWebhusayithi ukuyisebenzisa.

system_info.export_configuration_description: Olu khetho luvumela ukuba ukuthumezwe luthunyelo lonke uqwalaselo lwenkqubo yakho, ngaphandle kwamango. Uqwalaselo luya kukhutshelwa kwi-password ekhuselweyo ye-AES256 efihliweyo yifayile ye-zip. Unokufuna umsebenzi onje nge-7zip ukuya kwi-Deorppt.
system_info.export_schema_description: Olu khetho luvumela ukuba uthumele kwelinye ilizwe inkqubo yoqwalaselo yenkqubo yenkqubo (ubume bedatha). Oku kunokuba luncedo xa kuqwalaselwa isimo se-Yalal ye-Yalol kwaye yi-analogous kwi-schema yedatha.
system_info.import_config_description: Olu khetho luvumela ukuba ungenise isimo senkqubo yakho. Ukungenisa akongezwanga kwiseto esele ikho-kuyinto yonke. Le nkqubo yi-analogous kwindawo yokubuyisela inkcukacha.
system_info.details-description: Iinkcukacha malunga nesixokelelwano esiquka i-Web UI version esebenzayo kunye ne-ID yokuhlohla
system_info.db-details-description: Iinkcukacha ezisisiseko malunga nesiseko sedatha yangoku, kubandakanywa umamkeli kunye noguqulelo.
system_info.api-details-description: Ulwazi malunga ne-API yangoku, kuquka inguqulelo kunye nomninimzi.
system_info.license-details-description: Iinkcukacha malunga nayo nayiphi na ilayisensi esetyenziswayo ngoku.

tooltip.add_images_to_default_group: Yongeza ngokuzenzekelayo amashishini kwiqela elimiselweyo xa kuvuswa iindawo zokusebenza.
tooltip.agent_version: Esi seto sisetyenziselwa ukuthintela ukuba iinguqulelo ze-ASM ze-KaSM zivunyelwe ukuba zinxibelelane nomphathi.

tooltip.api_private_key: Isitshixo sabucala esisetyenziselwa ukutyikitya isicelo phakathi kwamacandelo e-KASM.
tooltip.api_public_cert: Isitshixo sikawonke-wonke esisetyenziswa ngamacandelo eKasm ukuqinisekisa iifowuni zangaphakathi ze-API.

tooltip.default_cpu_allocation_method: Icwangcisa isicwangciso sokulwa ulwabiwo lwe-CPU se-CPU kwimifanekiso eqingqiweyo. Iinketho ezifanelekileyo ziyi-quotas okanye izabelo.
tooltip.default_vm_rdp_connection_settings: Useto lonxibelelwano olungagqibekanga lweseshoni ye-VM ye-vm.
tooltip.default_vm_ssh_connection_settings: Useto lonxibelelwano olungagqibekanga lweseshoni ye-VM Ssh ssh ssh ssh.
tooltip.default_vm_vnc_connection_settings: Useto lonxibelelwano olungagqibekanga lweseshoni ye-VM Vnc.
tooltip.enable_kasm_auth: Funa izicelo zabaxhamli kwiKasm yomxholo njengokukhutshelwa kunye nokulayisha ukungqinisiswa kwethokheni yeseshoni yomsebenzisi.
tooltip.forward_inter_zone_agent_requests: Xa iiarhente zokunxibelelana kwindawo eyahlukileyo, izicelo zangaphambili kwidilesi yommeli we-proxy yendawo.
tooltip.guardian_interval: Inani lemizuzwana phakathi komphathi we-API yearhente ekhoyo, kunye nokufumaneka kwe-Kasm.
tooltip.guardian_provision_threads: Inani lemisoyitha umphathi we-API ye-API ye-TEARDOwn kunye nemisebenzi yokubonelela.
tooltip.hec_token: Ithokheni ye-splkenk isetyenziselwa ukungqinisisa kwezingodo kwiseva ye-splkenk.
tooltip.host_dead_expiration: Inani lemizuzwana ukusukela kwi-arhente yokugqibela ngaphambi kokuba iphawule njengokufileyo. Iiseva ezifileyo ziyatshatyalaliswa ngokuzenzekelayo ukuba zilungisiwe ngokwasemzimbeni.
tooltip.host_missing_expiration: Inani lemizuzwana ukusukela kwi-arhente yokugqibela ngaphambi kokuba iphawule njengokufileyo.
tooltip.http_method: Indlela ye-HTTP yokusebenzisa, amaxabiso afanelekileyo aposti kwaye abekwe. I-splhunk isebenzisa iposti ngelixa i-elasticsersearch API isetyenziswa
tooltip.https_insecure: Zibekele inyani ukuba iseva yokuloba ide ayinayo i-CRECT esayiniweyo yiGunya leSitifiketi sikaRhulumente.
tooltip.keepalive_expiration: Abathengi bathumela rhoqo izicelo zokugcina abantu xa bengena kwi-KASM. Elixabiso linani lemizuzwana i-Kasm iya kuhlala isebenza emva kokugcinwa kokugqibela kufunyenwe.
tooltip.launcher_background_url: I-URL esetyenziselwa ukucacisa umfanekiso wangasemva wesiqalo.
tooltip.log_host: Igama lenginginya okanye idilesi ye-IP yeseva yokuloga, ayisebenzi ekulongeni yangaphakathi.
tooltip.log_protocol: IProtokholi yokuLoga esetyenzisiweyo, evumelekileyo ingaphakathi, i-HTTPS, i-splank, kunye ne-elasticser
tooltip.log_retention: Inani leentsuku zokugcina izingodo zendawo yendawo. Isilumkiso-Jonga amaxwebhu eKasm ngaphambi kokuhlengahlengiswa.
tooltip.login_assistance: Yenza unxibelelwano lokungena ngemvume kwiphepha lokungena kwi-URL engenisiweyo. Ayiboniswanga ukuba ixabiso alinanto.
tooltip.manager_expiration: Inani lemizuzwana de umphathi athathelwe ingqalelo ngokusisigxina, apho irekhodiweyo uMphathi irekhodiweyo iya kususwa kwindawo yedatha. Ixabiso le-0 ikhubaza itsheki yokuphelelwa.
tooltip.max_login_attempts: Inani leenzame zokungena ezingasebenziyo ngaphambi kokuba i-akhawunti itshixiwe. Esi seto sisebenza kuphela kwiiakhawunti zasekhaya.
tooltip.minimize_local_logging: Xa usebenzisa isisombululo sokungena okude njenge-splhunk, nciphisa indawo yedatha yendawo yokungena kwi-scaldry efanelekileyo.
tooltip.primary_manager_timeout: Inani lemizuzwana de umphathi ophambili athathwa njengengafumaneki. Ukuba abanye abaphathi bayaphila, baya kuthatha indima eyintloko.
tooltip.provision_timeout: Elona xesha liphezulu lokulinda i-Auto-i-Auto-i-ADMS yokujonga kwaye ifumaneke. Emva kweli xesha kugqitywe, i-VM itshatyalalisiwe ngokuzenzekelayo.
tooltip.registration_token: Ithokheni esetyenziselwa ukuzibhalisa izinto ezintsha kukuhambisa.
tooltip.same_site: Qwalasela uphawu olufanayo lwe-cookie ye-piep yokuphendula i-HTTP. Izinketho ezifanelekileyo ze-lax, zingqongqo kwaye akukho.
tooltip.same_zone_reply: Ukuba isetiwe yinyani, umphathi uya kuphendula kuphela kwi-arhente yentliziyo noluhlu lwabaphathi kwimimandla efanayo neyodwa. Kungenjalo kunikwa uluhlu lwabantu bonke abaphathi. Oku kuvumela iiarhente kumntu wokugcina abaphathi kwezinye iindawo.
tooltip.token: Ithokheni yokuqinisekisa esetyenziswe kunxibelelwano phakathi kweearhente ze-KASM kunye neseva ye-API.
tooltip.token_drift_max: Mingaphi imizuzu ekufuneka ikhutshelwe i-tota ivunyelwe ukuba ikhwele.
tooltip.update_check: Esi seto siyakuyeka umphathi ukuba akhangele uhlaziyo lwenkqubo ye-KASM.
tooltip.url_endpoint: IPROPIGE SPROGE, inokwenzeka / yenkonzo / inkonzo / umqokeleli / umsitho. Ye-elasticsersearch iya kuba yi-Index / _UC /.
tooltip.web_filter_update_url: I-URL esetyenziselwa ukuhlaziya idatha yecebo lokucoca iWebhu
tooltip.cleanup_orphaned_autoscale_servers: Ukuba inkqubo iphazamisekile okanye iimpazamo ngexesha le-AutoScaling iseva inokubonelelwa ngokuyinxenye kwaye inkqubo inokulahlekelwa ngumkhondo womncedisi oyinkedama. Oku kusebenzisa izibonelelo inkqubo engenakho ukubonelela ngazo. Ukwenza olu seto lusebenze kuvumela inkqubo ukuba isebenzise i-heuristics ukufumana nokutshabalalisa izixhobo eziziinkedama.
